.TH Man page : hsh

.SH NAME

.B hsh

.SH DESCRIPTION
This program is a simplified version of the shell.

.SH USAGE
To use this program in interactive mode, run "./hsh". A prompt ("$") will be presented to you where you can type commands.

.PP
- To execute a command, type the following and press enter.
.PP
$ [COMMAND] [ARGUMENT(S)]
.PP
- To exit the shell, type the following and press enter.
.PP
$ exit
.PP
- To display environment variables, type the following and press enter.
.PP
$ env

.PP
To use this program in non-interactive mode, type the following and press enter:
.PP
echo "[COMMAND] [ARGUMENT(S)]" | ./hsh

.SH EXAMPLES
In interactive mode :
.PP
$ ls
.PP
